    <item>
      <title>美联储永久按兵不动，但无需担心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-01/federal-reserve-is-on-perma-hold-but-there-s-no-need-to-worry-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在联邦公开市场委员会 (FOMC) 决策日，感觉美国央行行长的政策路径似乎已经被定价。由于债券损失可能受到限制，这甚至可能是一个买入机会。收益报告显示股市也不应承受过度压力。当然，风险在于通胀高于目标可能带来的压力——以及更高、更长时间的利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-01/federal-reserve-is-on-perma-hold-but-there-s-no-need-to-worry-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国监管机构讨论最早于八月敲定银行资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些批评人士呼吁放弃这一具有里程碑意义的计划，美联储和其他美国顶级监管机构仍在继续推进该计划，让大银行持有更多资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FTC 将在未来几天对埃克森美孚与先锋公司 600 亿美元的交易做出裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ftc-set-to-rule-on-60-billion-exxon-pioneer-deal-in-coming-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国联邦贸易委员会将在未来几天决定是否提起诉讼，阻止埃克森美孚公司以 600 亿美元收购先锋自然资源公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ftc-set-to-rule-on-60-billion-exxon-pioneer-deal-in-coming-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>观看鲍威尔关于三削减基本案例的语言：瓦特</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/watching-powell-language-on-three-cuts-base-case-watt-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银美国经济学家阿比盖尔·瓦特表示，她将关注美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔对三月份经济预测声明以及美联储三次降息基本预期的评论。她在“彭博今日市场”节目中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/watching-powell-language-on-three-cuts-base-case-watt-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:08:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
