    <item>
      <title>万事达卡下调预测，网络支出未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/mastercard-cuts-forecast-as-network-spending-misses-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万事达卡公司(Mastercard Inc.)下调了全年收入增长预期，理由是外汇不利因素超出了该公司的控制范围，因为该支付巨头网络第一季度的支出低于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/mastercard-cuts-forecast-as-network-spending-misses-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:26:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
